\overset{\left(**\right)}{=} & \frac{1}{\left|x-x_{0}\right|}\left|\stackrel[x_{0}]{x}{\int}f\left(t\right)-f\left(x_{0}\right)dt\right|\overset{\left(\diamondsuit\right)}{<}\\
